Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:03.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:06.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar Boy and... an octopus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Byro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:54.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guild wizards. Do you intend \Nto defy me to the bitter end?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a lot of fun, but it's about \Ntime to bring this to an end, hot boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd get sick ridin' on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not transportation! \NIt's obviously an octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's so gigantic, \Nit's clearly for transport!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick just lookin' at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! I've had it up to \Nhere with your gooey crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:42.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's flames d-disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:48.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot boy, Byro-sama negates \Nhis opponent's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?! \NIt's the first I've heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:12.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby! Come on! Grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His magic absorbs his opponent's \Nmagic and takes nourishment from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate him, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro-sama is busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fury of Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:04:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Ram, I open thee! Aries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:11.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that good enough?! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:14.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you did it, but \Nyou're totally tough to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Golden Bull, \NI open thee! Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san's in a pinch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,after protecting a beautiful \Ngirl from falling off a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:38.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice body! Hubba-hubba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:44.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! I'm not gonna bother gettin' \Nticked off at you, just get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll battle moooore fiercely than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:51.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I gonna lose to some cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not under her control?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:02.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, she can only control humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic doesn't work \Nagainst Celestial Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Taurus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:21.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl's got a nice \Nbody, too! Hubba-hubba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What the hell are you responding to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorta reluctant to attack a nice body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:34.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-neesan, your Celestial \NSpirits are all kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put it... Unique...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I can count on them... \Nbut their characters are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpio, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:55.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are! Leave it to me! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His character comes on strong, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:09.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's anything we \N{\i1}can{\i0} do when she's moving that fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take her down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she's the spitting image, \Nthat's not the Coco I knew in Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:29.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle this. Everyone, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanaloa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who's giving off \Nan enormous amount of magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An octopus...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reputation precedes you, Fairy \NTail's most powerful S Class Wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts Clive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:16.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are... but it looks \Nlike you've come to attack Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:20.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no business with your guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:26.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What an opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be my biggest scoop in the \Nhistory of the Weekly Sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:38.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after I start covering him for \N"Shadowing Gildarts for 24 Hours:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:43.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His Light and Dark Side", this \Ncoool situation comes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First a showdown after seven long years \Nand now this... it's too delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you want me to beat down \Nfirst? Your octopus? Or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist... I'll proceed \Nuntil you are eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk "elimination" or whatever, \Nand yet you're on the defensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I just nullified your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:28.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking precisely, I nullified your magic \Nagainst {\i1}me{\i0} and it discharged behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the nullified \Nmagic passed through you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then charged up again and had \Nan effect on the trees, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't have time to \Nface off against you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:47.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a mission to carry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eliminate you now. \NPlease, attack me at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scorpio! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are! I'm gonna go with a heavy hitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-neesan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! My attack hit {\i1}her{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you fight it, the more magic \Nit absorbs and the bigger it gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:30.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:35.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' to it! Ain't no way I'm \Ngonna lose against this blob!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:36.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate obstinate people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:48.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it doin' now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:55.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't only absorb power,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it can take on the properties \Nof what it's absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu is losing to fire?! \NI don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:22.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the more magic \Nit absorbs from the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the more powerful it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it, pretty blue cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:31.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but first do somethin' about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...this gooey fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hot boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My hound dog is truly the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:59.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up! Grow! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't half-bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He nullified it again! That's \Namazing! Too amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should clear the way by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:37.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Until you're out of my way then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, you're a pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you after, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you givin' our guild so much grief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving your guild grief? \NYou speak foolishly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:24.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike that Kain guy's controlling \Nmagic, she doesn't need to use hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But she can only control \None person at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:30.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the effect probably only \Nworks within a set distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I move far enough away, she probably \Nwon't be able to control me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:34.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but in these circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come clean, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:58.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something! Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's always on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I put you out of your misery, hot boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:21.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy... Pick me up and fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:35.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can run, but you \Ncan't hide, boy and cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:40.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Happy. Pitch me into that junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:46.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Natsu?! If I do \Nthat, it'll absorb your magic again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick an' tired of your slimy ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:04.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this... I'd say that's \Nthe very definition of "reckless"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:07.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb the power! Yes! Absorb it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:42.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo! My hound dog got a blowout \Nfrom eating too much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now what are you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this absorbs your ridiculous amount \Nof power, we'll both blow up, hot boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:15.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is happening because of your \Ndamn putty! It ain't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll use my hound dog's \Nincreased power to just protect {\i1}my{\i0} fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make your arm half-cooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I have anything to say about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coool! What a fool Jason is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:56.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Byro Cracy! He belongs \Nto the Legion Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legion Corps? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:06.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zentopia has followers all over Fiore, \Nnot to mention all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Legion Corps is a \Nsecret order of warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,from the dark side of their history!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it's comprised \Nof fierce soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who've been through training so harsh \Nthat not even a priest could endure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:26.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what does this secret \Norder want with Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:39.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail isn't a guild that \Ncan be crushed so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:45.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm not all that \Nworried, to be frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the members...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:57.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we only have business \Nwith Lucy Heartfilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What business with Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes tell me how serious you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But so are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no simple mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Archbishop of Zentopia has \Nentrusted us with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This crusade, so to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crusade?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:36.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed... It's very important \Nthat this crusade be carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:40.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in being a field \Nreporter if you die on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:07.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, this has taken more \Ntime than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's because we didn't have any \Ninformation about what you looked like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:23.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now. Come on over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:42.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you after Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, it's not Lucy \NHeartfilia herself that we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What we're looking for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit this bastard! Hit 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, why don't \Nyou let go of my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in \Nholding hands with a man
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and I hate both sweetness and obstinacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm holdin' \Nyour hand because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the only thing for it is to crush \Nyou until we get separated, hot boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:27.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, hot boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! I thought my arm was gonna snap off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you say when \Nsomeone saves your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You slant-eyed bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:55.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now we've got ice boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:01.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me any weird names! What \Nthe hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:06.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Gray! He's the Sugar Boy of Earthland!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:12.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on. Right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:23.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are after...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That clock hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is rare. It looks like \Nyou're having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:03.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't seem to get \Nthe better of this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more unpleasant \Nthan coming back home
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and finding the place overrun with scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:10.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a simpleton! Did you \Nreally think we wanted {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My father left me this keepsake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want it even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:35.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love stealing things that \Nare precious to people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.53,0:21:50.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:53.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Archbishop-sama, I got Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:02.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:10.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the clock hand has been obtained.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:19.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:23:59.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't gonna end with \NFairy Tail gettin' trounced!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they weren't after Lucy after \Nall, but that clock hand, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why they want that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:07.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:10.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet those jackasses are clock geeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:13.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, I don't think you're \Non the right track there...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Key of the Starry Sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're not geeks... Maybe it's a fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.40,0:24:23.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the big hand and little hand \Nform a golden triangle...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!
